{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":937,"text":"The work of a transportation commissioner"},{"time":3096,"text":"isn't just about stop signs and traffic signals."},{"time":6590,"text":"It involves the design of cities"},{"time":8764,"text":"and the design of city streets."},{"time":11160,"text":"Streets are some of the most valuable resources"},{"time":14131,"text":"that a city has, and yet it's an asset"},{"time":16909,"text":"that's largely hidden in plain sight."},{"time":19765,"text":"And the lesson from New York"},{"time":21346,"text":"over the past six years"},{"time":23004,"text":"is that you can update this asset."},{"time":25300,"text":"You can remake your streets quickly, inexpensively,"},{"time":28998,"text":"it can provide immediate benefits,"},{"time":31736,"text":"and it can be quite popular."},{"time":34337,"text":"You just need to look at them a little differently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37829,"text":"This is important because we live in an urban age."},{"time":41577,"text":"For the first time in history,"},{"time":43656,"text":"most people live in cities,"},{"time":46421,"text":"and the U.N. estimates that over the next 40 years,"},{"time":49984,"text":"the population is going to double on the planet."},{"time":52885,"text":"So the design of cities is a key issue for our future."},{"time":57328,"text":"Mayor Bloomberg recognized this"},{"time":58913,"text":"when he launched PlaNYC in 2007."},{"time":62152,"text":"The plan recognized that cities"},{"time":64865,"text":"are in a global marketplace,"},{"time":66987,"text":"and that if we're going to continue to grow and thrive"},{"time":69712,"text":"and to attract the million more people"},{"time":73015,"text":"that are expected to move here,"},{"time":74615,"text":"we need to focus on the quality of life"},{"time":77866,"text":"and the efficiency of our infrastructure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81534,"text":"For many cities, our streets have been"},{"time":83177,"text":"in a kind of suspended animation for generations."},{"time":87286,"text":"This is a picture of Times Square in the '50s,"},{"time":90862,"text":"and despite all of the technological innovation,"},{"time":94841,"text":"cultural changes, political changes,"},{"time":97290,"text":"this is Times Square in 2008."},{"time":99545,"text":"Not much has changed in those 50 years."},{"time":103918,"text":"So we worked hard to refocus our agenda,"},{"time":106981,"text":"to maximize efficient mobility,"},{"time":109596,"text":"providing more room for buses, more room for bikes,"},{"time":113177,"text":"more room for people to enjoy the city,"},{"time":116236,"text":"and to make our streets as safe as they can be"},{"time":118471,"text":"for everybody that uses them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121579,"text":"We set out a clear action plan"},{"time":124067,"text":"with goals and benchmarks."},{"time":126763,"text":"Having goals is important,"},{"time":128981,"text":"because if you want to change and steer the ship"},{"time":133102,"text":"of a big city in a new direction,"},{"time":135725,"text":"you need to know where you're going and why."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139921,"text":"The design of a street can tell you everything"},{"time":142174,"text":"about what's expected on it."},{"time":144523,"text":"In this case, it's expected that you shelter in place."},{"time":148524,"text":"The design of this street is really"},{"time":150461,"text":"to maximize the movement of cars"},{"time":153121,"text":"moving as quickly as possible"},{"time":154849,"text":"from point A to point B,"},{"time":156672,"text":"and it misses all the other ways"},{"time":158564,"text":"that a street is used."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160991,"text":"When we started out, we did some early surveys"},{"time":163942,"text":"about how our streets were used,"},{"time":165987,"text":"and we found that New York City was largely"},{"time":167983,"text":"a city without seats."},{"time":170114,"text":"Pictures like this, people perched"},{"time":172498,"text":"on a fire hydrant, not the mark of a world-class city."},{"time":176671,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":178959,"text":"It's not great for parents with kids."},{"time":181435,"text":"It's not great for seniors. It's not great for retailers."},{"time":184671,"text":"It's probably not good for the fire hydrants."},{"time":187712,"text":"Certainly not good for the police department."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190764,"text":"So we worked hard to change that balance,"},{"time":193773,"text":"and probably the best example of our new approach"},{"time":197108,"text":"is in Times Square."},{"time":198743,"text":"Three hundred and fifty thousand people a day"},{"time":202573,"text":"walk through Times Square,"},{"time":204283,"text":"and people had tried for years to make changes."},{"time":206773,"text":"They changed signals, they changed lanes,"},{"time":209161,"text":"everything they could do to make Times Square work better."},{"time":212064,"text":"It was dangerous, hard to cross the street."},{"time":214986,"text":"It was chaotic."},{"time":216707,"text":"And so, none of those approaches worked,"},{"time":219489,"text":"so we took a different approach, a bigger approach,"},{"time":221538,"text":"looked at our street differently."},{"time":223207,"text":"And so we did a six-month pilot."},{"time":226780,"text":"We closed Broadway from 42nd Street to 47th Street"},{"time":231036,"text":"and created two and a half acres"},{"time":233570,"text":"of new pedestrian space."},{"time":236346,"text":"And the temporary materials are an important part"},{"time":239513,"text":"of the program, because we were able to show"},{"time":242938,"text":"how it worked."},{"time":244307,"text":"And I work for a data-driven mayor, as you probably know."},{"time":247286,"text":"So it was all about the data."},{"time":249122,"text":"So if it worked better for traffic, if it was better for mobility,"},{"time":252295,"text":"if it was safer, better for business, we would keep it,"},{"time":254648,"text":"and if it didn't work, no harm, no foul,"},{"time":257379,"text":"we could put it back the way that it was,"},{"time":259269,"text":"because these were temporary materials."},{"time":260530,"text":"And that was a very big part of the buy-in,"},{"time":263439,"text":"much less anxiety when you think that something"},{"time":265582,"text":"can be put back."},{"time":267453,"text":"But the results were overwhelming."},{"time":269607,"text":"Traffic moved better. It was much safer."},{"time":272527,"text":"Five new flagship stores opened."},{"time":274934,"text":"It's been a total home run."},{"time":276807,"text":"Times Square is now one of the top 10"},{"time":279390,"text":"retail locations on the planet."},{"time":282021,"text":"And this is an important lesson,"},{"time":284455,"text":"because it doesn't need to be a zero-sum game"},{"time":287553,"text":"between moving traffic and creating public space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292078,"text":"Every project has its surprises,"},{"time":294893,"text":"and one of the big surprises with Times Square"},{"time":297546,"text":"was how quickly people flocked to the space."},{"time":301226,"text":"We put out the orange barrels,"},{"time":303284,"text":"and people just materialized immediately into the street."},{"time":306892,"text":"It was like a Star Trek episode, you know?"},{"time":308933,"text":"They weren't there before, and then zzzzzt!"},{"time":311262,"text":"All the people arrived."},{"time":312640,"text":"Where they'd been, I don't know, but they were there."},{"time":315398,"text":"And this actually posed an immediate challenge for us,"},{"time":318542,"text":"because the street furniture had not yet arrived."},{"time":322058,"text":"So we went to a hardware store"},{"time":324680,"text":"and bought hundreds of lawn chairs,"},{"time":327027,"text":"and we put those lawn chairs out on the street."},{"time":330219,"text":"And the lawn chairs became the talk of the town."},{"time":334115,"text":"It wasn't about that we'd closed Broadway to cars."},{"time":336999,"text":"It was about those lawn chairs."},{"time":338358,"text":"\"What did you think about the lawn chairs?\""},{"time":339889,"text":"\"Do you like the color of the lawn chairs?\""},{"time":341566,"text":"So if you've got a big, controversial project,"},{"time":345332,"text":"think about lawn chairs."},{"time":347043,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":349953,"text":"This is the final design for Times Square,"},{"time":352450,"text":"and it will create a level surface,"},{"time":354990,"text":"sidewalk to sidewalk,"},{"time":356674,"text":"beautiful pavers that have studs in them"},{"time":358902,"text":"to reflect the light from the billboards,"},{"time":360940,"text":"creating a great new energy on the street,"},{"time":363653,"text":"and we think it's going to really create"},{"time":365770,"text":"a great place, a new crossroads of the world"},{"time":367928,"text":"that is worthy of its name."},{"time":369451,"text":"And we will be cutting the ribbon on this,"},{"time":370952,"text":"the first phase, this December."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374554,"text":"With all of our projects, our public space projects,"},{"time":377011,"text":"we work closely with local businesses"},{"time":379224,"text":"and local merchant groups"},{"time":380755,"text":"who maintain the spaces, move the furniture,"},{"time":384071,"text":"take care of the plants."},{"time":385492,"text":"This is in front of Macy's, and they were"},{"time":387511,"text":"a big supporter of this new approach,"},{"time":389625,"text":"because they understood that more people on foot"},{"time":394472,"text":"is better for business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396453,"text":"And we've done these projects all across the city"},{"time":399123,"text":"in all kinds of neighborhoods."},{"time":400735,"text":"This is in Bed-Stuy, Brooklyn,"},{"time":402861,"text":"and you can see the short leg that was there,"},{"time":404953,"text":"used for cars, that's not really needed."},{"time":407203,"text":"So what we did is we painted over the street,"},{"time":410792,"text":"put down epoxy gravel, and connected the triangle"},{"time":414123,"text":"to the storefronts on Grand Avenue,"},{"time":416118,"text":"created a great new public space,"},{"time":418116,"text":"and it's been great for businesses"},{"time":420130,"text":"along Grand Avenue."},{"time":421713,"text":"We did the same thing in DUMBO, in Brooklyn,"},{"time":424869,"text":"and this is one of our first projects that we did,"},{"time":427297,"text":"and we took an underutilized,"},{"time":429892,"text":"pretty dingy-looking parking lot"},{"time":432573,"text":"and used some paint and planters"},{"time":435825,"text":"to transform it over a weekend."},{"time":438711,"text":"And in the three years since we've implemented the project,"},{"time":441669,"text":"retail sales have increased 172 percent."},{"time":446423,"text":"And that's twice that of adjacent areas in the same neighborhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451295,"text":"We've moved very, very quickly"},{"time":453444,"text":"with paint and temporary materials."},{"time":455693,"text":"Instead of waiting"},{"time":456950,"text":"through years of planning studies"},{"time":459773,"text":"and computer models to get something done,"},{"time":462151,"text":"we've done it with paint and temporary materials."},{"time":464886,"text":"And the proof is not in a computer model."},{"time":467236,"text":"It is in the real-world performance of the street."},{"time":470201,"text":"You can have fun with paint."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473197,"text":"All told, we've created over 50 pedestrian plazas"},{"time":477430,"text":"in all five boroughs across the city."},{"time":480205,"text":"We've repurposed 26 acres of active car lanes"},{"time":485011,"text":"and turned them into new pedestrian space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489007,"text":"I think one of the successes is in its emulation."},{"time":492448,"text":"You're seeing this kind of approach,"},{"time":493989,"text":"since we've painted Times Square,"},{"time":495544,"text":"you've seen this approach in Boston, in Chicago,"},{"time":498574,"text":"in San Francisco, in Mexico City,"},{"time":501073,"text":"Buenos Aires, you name it."},{"time":502636,"text":"This is actually in Los Angeles,"},{"time":504985,"text":"and they actually copied even the green dots"},{"time":508608,"text":"that we had on the streets."},{"time":510633,"text":"But I can't underscore enough"},{"time":512743,"text":"how much more quickly this enables you to move"},{"time":515320,"text":"over traditional construction methods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518442,"text":"We also brought this quick-acting approach"},{"time":520602,"text":"to our cycling program,"},{"time":522150,"text":"and in six years turned cycling"},{"time":524666,"text":"into a real transportation option in New York."},{"time":527905,"text":"I think it's fair to say --"},{"time":529602,"text":"(Applause) --"},{"time":534841,"text":"it used to be a fairly scary place to ride a bike,"},{"time":538305,"text":"and now New York has become"},{"time":539863,"text":"one of the cycling capitals in the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543908,"text":"And we moved quickly to create an interconnected"},{"time":547904,"text":"network of lanes."},{"time":550339,"text":"You can see the map in 2007."},{"time":552700,"text":"This is how it looked in 2013"},{"time":554894,"text":"after we built out 350 miles of on-street bike lanes."},{"time":559490,"text":"I love this because it looks so easy."},{"time":561507,"text":"You just click it, and they're there."},{"time":565406,"text":"We also brought new designs to the street."},{"time":568417,"text":"We created the first parking-protected bike lane"},{"time":571754,"text":"in the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573326,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":574853,"text":"We protected bikers by floating parking lanes,"},{"time":578124,"text":"and it's been great."},{"time":579637,"text":"Bike volumes have spiked."},{"time":581364,"text":"Injuries to all users, pedestrians, cyclists, drivers,"},{"time":583998,"text":"are all down 50 percent."},{"time":585789,"text":"And we've built 30 miles of these protected bike lanes,"},{"time":589052,"text":"and now you're seeing them pop up"},{"time":590591,"text":"all over the country."},{"time":592460,"text":"And you can see here that this strategy has worked."},{"time":595317,"text":"The blue line is the number of cyclists,"},{"time":596969,"text":"soaring."},{"time":597973,"text":"The green line is the number of bike lanes."},{"time":599916,"text":"And the yellow line is the number of injuries,"},{"time":602412,"text":"which has remained essentially flat."},{"time":604897,"text":"After this big expansion, you've seen"},{"time":607765,"text":"no net increase in injuries,"},{"time":609615,"text":"and so there is something to that axiom"},{"time":612271,"text":"that there is safety in numbers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":615518,"text":"Not everybody liked the new bike lanes,"},{"time":618650,"text":"and there was a lawsuit and somewhat"},{"time":620922,"text":"of a media frenzy a couple years ago."},{"time":623894,"text":"One Brooklyn paper called this bike lane"},{"time":626141,"text":"that we have on Prospect Park West"},{"time":628595,"text":"\"the most contested piece of land"},{"time":630483,"text":"outside of the Gaza Strip.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":632455,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":635834,"text":"And this is what we had done."},{"time":637754,"text":"So if you dig below the headlines, though,"},{"time":642760,"text":"you'll see that the people were far ahead of the press,"},{"time":645653,"text":"far ahead of the politicians."},{"time":647901,"text":"In fact, I think most politicians would be happy"},{"time":650089,"text":"to have those kind of poll numbers."},{"time":652240,"text":"Sixty-four percent of New Yorkers support these bike lanes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655318,"text":"This summer, we launched Citi Bike,"},{"time":657297,"text":"the largest bike share program in the United States,"},{"time":659880,"text":"with 6,000 bikes"},{"time":661764,"text":"and 330 stations located next to one another."},{"time":665326,"text":"Since we've launched the program,"},{"time":667334,"text":"three million trips have been taken."},{"time":669002,"text":"People have ridden seven million miles."},{"time":671771,"text":"That's 280 times around the globe."},{"time":674633,"text":"And so with this little blue key,"},{"time":676704,"text":"you can unlock the keys to the city"},{"time":679337,"text":"and this brand new transportation option."}]},{"cues":[{"time":681893,"text":"And daily usage just continues to soar."},{"time":684252,"text":"What has happened is the average daily ridership"},{"time":686997,"text":"on the streets of New York is 36,000 people."},{"time":689703,"text":"The high that we've had so far is 44,000 in August."},{"time":692735,"text":"Yesterday, 40,000 people used Citi Bike in New York City."},{"time":696624,"text":"The bikes are being used six times a day."},{"time":698586,"text":"And I think you also see it in the kinds of riders"},{"time":701367,"text":"that are on the streets."},{"time":702722,"text":"In the past, it looked like the guy on the left,"},{"time":705096,"text":"ninja-clad bike messenger."},{"time":708101,"text":"And today, cyclists look"},{"time":711938,"text":"like New York City looks."},{"time":714109,"text":"It's diverse -- young, old, black, white,"},{"time":717291,"text":"women, kids, all getting on a bike."},{"time":720309,"text":"It's an affordable, safe, convenient way to get around."},{"time":723326,"text":"Quite radical."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725416,"text":"We've also brought this approach to our buses,"},{"time":728558,"text":"and New York City has the largest bus fleet in North America,"},{"time":731995,"text":"the slowest bus speeds."},{"time":733436,"text":"As everybody knows,"},{"time":734515,"text":"you can walk across town faster"},{"time":736917,"text":"than you can take the bus."},{"time":738137,"text":"And so we focused on the most congested areas"},{"time":740939,"text":"of New York City,"},{"time":742364,"text":"built out six bus rapid transit lines,"},{"time":745295,"text":"57 miles of new speedy bus lanes."},{"time":748588,"text":"You pay at a kiosk before you get on the bus."},{"time":751318,"text":"We've got dedicated lanes that keep cars out"},{"time":753704,"text":"because they get ticketed by a camera"},{"time":755830,"text":"if they use that lane,"},{"time":757343,"text":"and it's been a huge success."}]},{"cues":[{"time":760985,"text":"I think one of my very favorite moments"},{"time":763025,"text":"as transportation commissioner was the day"},{"time":765311,"text":"that we launched Citi Bike,"},{"time":766808,"text":"and I was riding Citi Bike up First Avenue"},{"time":769858,"text":"in my protected bike lane,"},{"time":771218,"text":"and I looked over and I saw pedestrians"},{"time":773594,"text":"standing safely on the pedestrian islands,"},{"time":776222,"text":"and the traffic was flowing,"},{"time":778586,"text":"birds were singing --"},{"time":780536,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":781891,"text":"the buses were speeding up their dedicated lanes."},{"time":784977,"text":"It was just fantastic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":788675,"text":"And this is how it looked six years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":791546,"text":"And so, I think that the lesson that we have"},{"time":794990,"text":"from New York is that it's possible"},{"time":798469,"text":"to change your streets quickly,"},{"time":801177,"text":"it's not expensive, it can provide immediate benefits,"},{"time":805171,"text":"and it can be quite popular."},{"time":807525,"text":"You just need to reimagine your streets."},{"time":810804,"text":"They're hidden in plain sight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812869,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":814267,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}